3892:Datestamp identifying a reliquary — the GAR namespace holding a coherent set of mirrored tool images for builder use.
3895:Mints once at {rbtgo_depot_inscribe} time and serves both as the GAR path segment (`{gar_reliquaries_namespace}/«STAMP»/...`) and the per-tool tag, so a single value identifies the namespace and pins every member.
3901:Format: `«KIND»YYMMDDHHMMSS`, where `«KIND»` is the kind-letter (`b` bole, `t` tool, `r` reliquary, `w` wsl, `vw`/`vn` podvm) and the datestamp is second-granular (e.g., `b260602120000`).

